	<longdescription lang="en">
		Unvanquished is a fast-paced, futuristic FPS with RTS elements,
		pitting technologically advanced humans against hordes of highly
		adaptable aliens. The player can choose from either team,
		providing a fresh gameplay experience on both sides of the
		conflict.
	</longdescription>
